A = [1 2 1; 0 -3 1; 1 1 1]
B = [1 3 0; 0 2 0; -1 0 1]
C = [3 0 2; -2 1 -1; -1 1 2]
D = [1 3 5; 4 0 -2; 0 0 1]
X = [0.5 0 0; 4 -2 8; 15/2 -4 11]

E = (A*X)+B
F = (C*X) - X + D

E == F

library(matlib)

A = rbind(c(1,1,2),c(2,4,-3),c(3,6,-5))
b = c(9,1,0)
AB = cbind(A,b)

showEqn(A,b)
## 1*x1 + 1*x2 + 2*x3  =  9 
## 2*x1 + 4*x2 - 3*x3  =  1 
## 3*x1 + 6*x2 - 5*x3  =  0
plotEqn3d(A,b, xlim = c(-3,3), ylim = c(0,6))

Solve(A, b, fractions = TRUE)
## x1      =  1 
##   x2    =  2 
##     x3  =  3
echelon(AB, verbose = TRUE, fractions = T)

A = rbind(c(0,4),c(2,1))
B = rbind(c(1,-1),c(2,3))
C = rbind(c(1,2),c(3,-2))
D = rbind(c(-2,1),c(-1,1))
I = diag(1, nrow = 2, ncol = 2)
M = A-(C+D)
N = 3*(D-B)+10*I
X = solve(M,N)
Z = solve(M)%*%N
